            </ul>
        </aside>
        <main class="content">
            <section class="contact-section">
                <h1>Contact Us</h1>
                <p>If you have any questions, feedback, or just want to get in touch, feel free to reach out to us through the following channels:</p>
                <h2>Email</h2>
                <p>You can email us at <a href="https://mail.google.com/mail/?view=cm&fs=1&to=dhruvmali345@gmail.com" target="_blank">dhruvmali345@gmail.com</a></p>
                <h2>LinkedIn</h2>
                <p>Connect with us on LinkedIn: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/dhruv-mali-38b519280/" target="_blank">Linked IN !!</a></p>
                <h2>Other Social Media</h2>
                <p>Follow us on Twitter: <a href="https://x.com/DhruvMali17" target="_blank">@DhruvMali17</a></p>
                
                <p>Follow us on Instagram: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/justtdhruvv/" target="_blank">@justtdhruvv</a></p>
                
                <h2>Contact Request Form</h2>
                <form action="/submit-contact-request" method="POST">
                    <label for="contactName">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="contactName" name="contactName" required>
                    
                    <label for="contactEmail">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="contactEmail" name="contactEmail" required>
                    
                    <label for="contactPhone">Mobile Number</label>
                    <input type="tel" id="contactPhone" name="contactPhone" required>
                    
                    <button type="submit">Submit Request</button>
                </form>

                <% if (message) { %>
                    <p><%= message %></p>
                <% } %>

            </section>
        </main>
